1736379.name: Traumpfad München-Venedig
1736379.fixme: In bing the roundabout in Belluno (Viale Europa) does not look like to be a good place for walking/crossing the streets. But first better mapping of roundabout itself is needed, before route can be improved.
1736379.note:1: In the valley south of Wattens and Wattenberg there are two alternate ways: Alternative 1 (more track like according to bing);Alternative 2 (more path like according to bing).
1736379.note:2: Relation is ordered: \"Mainroute north\"+ Alternative 1;Alternative 2 + MainRoute south;having an interrupt between Alternative 1 and Alternative 2
1736379.note:3: There is an alternate route near Rocca Pietore/Pezze. Relation is orddered: MainRoute from West+Alternate 1;Gap;Alternate 2+MainRoute to East.
1736379.note:4: There is a small alternative (single way) near Masare. Relation is ordered: Main from NW+Alternate 1;Gap;Alternate 2 + Main to SW
1736379.note:5: There is an alternate between Weitental/Vallarga and Lahner. Relation is sorted: MainRoute from north+Alternative 1;Gap;Alternative 2+MainRoute to south
1736379.note:6: There is an alternative around Pfunders/Fundres. Relation is sorted: MainRoute from north+alternate 1;gap;Alternate 2+MainRoute to south
